01:33:41,180 --> 01:33:42,180
Second one.

2409
01:33:42,180 --> 01:33:45,059
Well, actually the 25 was the worst of the two, so.

2410
01:33:45,059 --> 01:33:46,619
Nice.

2411
01:33:46,619 --> 01:33:48,059
Not too shabby.

2412
01:33:48,059 --> 01:33:50,260
And that'll be 14 damage.

2413
01:33:51,340 --> 01:33:52,180
Okay.

2414
01:33:52,180 --> 01:33:53,300
And I guess I'll keep trying to like

2415
01:33:53,340 --> 01:33:55,860
push skeletons off me to wrap up my turn.

2416
01:33:55,860 --> 01:33:57,579
Oh, I should roll my wisdom save.

2417
01:33:57,579 --> 01:33:58,699
Yep.

2418
01:33:58,699 --> 01:33:59,539
Hey.

2419
01:34:00,500 --> 01:34:01,940
Oh God.

2420
01:34:01,940 --> 01:34:02,980
I don't know where the dice went.

2421
01:34:02,980 --> 01:34:04,380
Hang on.

2422
01:34:04,380 --> 01:34:05,220
Not good enough.

2423
01:34:06,539 --> 01:34:07,380
Fair enough.

2424
01:34:07,380 --> 01:34:09,380
This dice is just not good enough.

2425
01:34:09,380 --> 01:34:11,659
Novrith goes and swings at you.

2426
01:34:11,659 --> 01:34:14,659
First action is 26 flint.

2427
01:34:14,659 --> 01:34:15,980
Second one's an eight.

2428
01:34:15,980 --> 01:34:19,820
You're gonna take eight slashing damage.

2429
01:34:19,820 --> 01:34:20,900
I will take five of it.

2430
01:34:20,900 --> 01:34:22,780
And then Varnax, you are up.

2431
01:34:23,900 --> 01:34:27,060
I am going, now that I've moved up to Lipsynche,

2432
01:34:27,060 --> 01:34:30,180
I'm gonna say, it's quite a flattering form you've taken.

2433
01:34:31,140 --> 01:34:34,140
Perhaps it is, I can only get away with one this time.

2434
01:34:34,140 --> 01:34:37,100
And I'm going to attempt and grapple.

2435
01:34:37,100 --> 01:34:37,940
Yes.

2436
01:34:38,820 --> 01:34:40,980
Very, very, hitting myself.

2437
01:34:40,980 --> 01:34:42,380
That was sensual.

2438
01:34:42,380 --> 01:34:43,380
About time.

2439
01:34:43,380 --> 01:34:44,220
Right?

2440
01:34:45,540 --> 01:34:46,380
Grapple.

2441
01:34:46,380 --> 01:34:47,780
Yeah, I'm going to attempt a grapple.

2442
01:34:47,780 --> 01:34:49,700
Is that just like a strength contest?

2443
01:34:51,540 --> 01:34:53,380
Yeah, yeah, straight, straight.

2444
01:34:55,500 --> 01:34:56,340
Okay.

2445
01:34:56,340 --> 01:35:00,300
Against all odds, my tiny gnome has rolled a 19.

2446
01:35:01,340 --> 01:35:02,820
You're not tiny anymore, though.

2447
01:35:02,820 --> 01:35:04,940
Oh, that's true, but yeah, okay.

2448
01:35:04,940 --> 01:35:05,940
Oh yeah.

2449
01:35:05,940 --> 01:35:10,380
So, do y'all do, who would win at it as a 19 versus 19?

2450
01:35:10,380 --> 01:35:13,580
Of course we'd tie, we're the same man right now.

2451
01:35:13,580 --> 01:35:14,980
Right? Exactly.

2452
01:35:14,980 --> 01:35:16,820
Maybe it's, they've got each other

2453
01:35:16,820 --> 01:35:19,340
and they're just locked in this.

2454
01:35:19,340 --> 01:35:21,539
It's like a cobra and a mongoose.

2455
01:35:21,539 --> 01:35:24,539
Or, yeah, yeah, roll again

2456
01:35:24,539 --> 01:35:26,500
because you have the same modifier, so.

2457
01:35:26,500 --> 01:35:28,659
We'll see who gets tired first.

2458
01:35:28,659 --> 01:35:30,140
Okay. Roll for tired.

2459
01:35:33,180 --> 01:35:34,300
14.

2460
01:35:34,300 --> 01:35:35,420
It's a 15 this time.

2461
01:35:35,420 --> 01:35:36,260
No.

2462
01:35:36,260 --> 01:35:38,579
Ah! So close.

2463
01:35:38,579 --> 01:35:39,420
So close.

2464
01:35:40,779 --> 01:35:43,260
Now that I've got lip-synchy grappled,

2465
01:35:43,260 --> 01:35:46,260
I am going to use whatever movement I have

2466
01:35:46,260 --> 01:35:48,860
to move us towards the portal and jump in.

2467
01:35:48,899 --> 01:35:52,099
And as I do, I say,

2468
01:35:52,099 --> 01:35:53,779
if you've lost something in this world,

2469
01:35:53,779 --> 01:35:56,819
Orcus can provide it back to you.

2470
01:35:56,819 --> 01:35:59,219
Follow his path and you'll find everything

2471
01:35:59,219 --> 01:36:00,819
that you've been looking for.

2472
01:36:00,819 --> 01:36:03,779
Maybe even companions you've lost.

2473
01:36:04,659 --> 01:36:06,219
Who knows what's on the other side,

2474
01:36:06,219 --> 01:36:08,539
but we're about to find out.

2475
01:36:08,539 --> 01:36:13,380
And I drop back into the portal with lip-synchy.

2476
01:36:13,380 --> 01:36:18,380
The two of them fall backwards into the portal

2477
01:36:18,579 --> 01:36:20,100
and get sucked in.

2478
01:36:20,100 --> 01:36:22,180
And in an explosion of energy,

2479
01:36:22,180 --> 01:36:26,060
it shoots up and echoes through the room

2480
01:36:26,060 --> 01:36:27,300
and sucks back in.

2481
01:36:27,300 --> 01:36:29,859
The skeletons get sucked in by the force behind them.

2482
01:36:29,859 --> 01:36:32,060
Both of you make a strength saving throw.

2483
01:36:33,940 --> 01:36:35,579
Ones. Ones.

2484
01:36:35,579 --> 01:36:37,180
Not 20.

2485
01:36:37,180 --> 01:36:38,020
Okay. Fuck.

2486
01:36:38,020 --> 01:36:39,020
Oh, wow.

2487
01:36:39,020 --> 01:36:39,859
13.

2488
01:36:39,859 --> 01:36:41,819
Still at disadvantage because you're sickened.

2489
01:36:41,819 --> 01:36:43,060
Oh, all right.

2490
01:36:44,940 --> 01:36:45,779
Well, I don't know if I'd be there.

2491
01:36:45,779 --> 01:36:47,699
13 was better.

2492
01:36:47,779 --> 01:36:49,859
Or was worse than what was rolled.

2493
01:36:49,859 --> 01:36:53,899
Flint, because of the amount of skeletons around you,

2494
01:36:53,899 --> 01:36:56,539
you get sucked down and kind of skid along the ground

2495
01:36:56,539 --> 01:36:58,500
as they get sucked behind you

2496
01:36:58,500 --> 01:37:01,979
and explode in dust and debris.

2497
01:37:01,979 --> 01:37:03,579
You hear from down the hall,

2498
01:37:03,579 --> 01:37:07,099
the groaning zombies amassing

2499
01:37:07,099 --> 01:37:11,019
as the walls echo with this explosion.

2500
01:37:11,019 --> 01:37:13,619
And you look down in the middle of the room

2501
01:37:13,619 --> 01:37:16,300
and you see lip-synchy's bracer

2502
01:37:16,340 --> 01:37:18,100
sitting where the portal shut.

2503
01:37:29,940 --> 01:37:32,739
We flash to lip-synchy and Vorunax

2504
01:37:32,739 --> 01:37:35,980
jumping backwards through the open portal.

2505
01:37:35,980 --> 01:37:39,539
The two are seen falling through darkness.

2506
01:37:39,539 --> 01:37:43,500
The sound of a crying wind whipping past them

2507
01:37:43,500 --> 01:37:46,659
before we see lip-synchy crashing to the ground,

2508
01:37:46,659 --> 01:37:47,659
hitting hard.

2509
01:37:49,819 --> 01:37:54,220
The sound of bones crunching echoes out into the stale air.

2510
01:37:55,819 --> 01:37:59,260
Lying motionless, what do you do?

2511
01:38:00,819 --> 01:38:01,819
Why did you?

2512
01:38:03,020 --> 01:38:05,180
I can't, can I even move?

2513
01:38:05,180 --> 01:38:06,579
Am I like?

2514
01:38:06,579 --> 01:38:10,579
Yeah, after a moment of catching your breath,

2515
01:38:10,579 --> 01:38:12,460
you are able to move.

2516
01:38:12,460 --> 01:38:15,859
Then I guess I will stand up and look around

2517
01:38:15,859 --> 01:38:18,579
and see if I can see what I can see.

2518
01:38:20,619 --> 01:38:25,220
As the moment passes, you give yourself just a feel over.

2519
01:38:25,220 --> 01:38:28,020
The sound of the breaking bones wasn't yourself.

2520
01:38:29,060 --> 01:38:30,739
It was the ground around you.

2521
01:38:31,699 --> 01:38:34,579
You put your hands down to lift yourself up

2522
01:38:34,579 --> 01:38:35,899
and look around where you are

2523
01:38:35,899 --> 01:38:38,380
and you see that the ground is littered

2524
01:38:38,380 --> 01:38:40,060
with skeletal remains.

2525
01:38:42,500 --> 01:38:46,060
You look out beyond and you strain to see,

2526
01:38:46,060 --> 01:38:50,020
even being able to see in darkness as you can.

2527
01:38:50,020 --> 01:38:52,819
You hear strong, slow footsteps

2528
01:38:52,819 --> 01:38:55,340
coming closer from behind you.

2529
01:38:55,340 --> 01:38:57,460
As you hear Vorunax say,

2530
01:38:57,460 --> 01:39:00,340
Welcome to the promised land, Miss Pip Diggins.

2531
01:39:00,340 --> 01:39:04,220
This is Thanatos, the home of our demon prince

2532
01:39:04,220 --> 01:39:07,779
and lord of the undead, Orcus.

2533
01:39:07,779 --> 01:39:10,779
Why did you bring me to this cursed place?

2534
01:39:10,819 --> 01:39:14,699
He gives a low chuckle as you look out

2535
01:39:14,699 --> 01:39:17,899
and your eyes begin to focus a little more

2536
01:39:17,899 --> 01:39:20,939
and you see your surroundings a little more clearly.

2537
01:39:20,939 --> 01:39:24,300
There's rolling hills in front of you.

2538
01:39:24,300 --> 01:39:27,019
You see the silhouette of Vorunax

2539
01:39:27,019 --> 01:39:31,460
and the sound of moans and hisses and cries

2540
01:39:31,460 --> 01:39:33,500
rush over the rolling hills,

2541
01:39:33,500 --> 01:39:36,179
the rubble, the bones and barren rock.

2542
01:39:36,179 --> 01:39:39,179
And as they hit you and surround you,

2543
01:39:39,220 --> 01:39:43,020
you begin to feel dread flow through your being.

2544
01:39:44,260 --> 01:39:47,420
You look out over, spinning and reeling

2545
01:39:47,420 --> 01:39:50,900
and you see a sea filled with not water,

2546
01:39:50,900 --> 01:39:55,420
but a roiling, churning ocean of black-red blood.

2547
01:39:57,100 --> 01:40:00,619
The stench of copper, death and decay hits you,

2548
01:40:00,619 --> 01:40:02,900
causing you to gag on the air you breathe

2549
01:40:02,900 --> 01:40:06,740
as you feel your own life beginning to leave your body.

2550
01:40:07,739 --> 01:40:10,739
You hear Vorunax chuckle again

2551
01:40:10,739 --> 01:40:13,739
as you gasp for air and fall to your knees

2552
01:40:13,739 --> 01:40:17,219
and he says, not yet.

2553
01:40:17,219 --> 01:40:21,739
Suddenly, a snap rings out and all goes silent.

2554
01:40:23,739 --> 01:40:26,739
You find yourself in a new room.

2555
01:40:26,739 --> 01:40:28,739
You gasp for air.

2556
01:40:29,739 --> 01:40:34,739
Stale as it is, you feel it's no longer killing you.

2557
01:40:37,219 --> 01:40:41,420
Vorunax speaks from the far side of this new space.

2558
01:40:41,420 --> 01:40:43,699
You look up and you see him standing illuminated

2559
01:40:43,699 --> 01:40:46,739
by a red light through a door and he says,

2560
01:40:46,739 --> 01:40:49,099
there are some beings with special abilities

2561
01:40:49,099 --> 01:40:51,739
that the demon prince is taken an interest in.

2562
01:40:51,739 --> 01:40:55,179
You, you are one of those beings.

2563
01:40:55,179 --> 01:40:57,859
Your time will come, but for now, Miss Pip Diggins,

2564
01:40:57,859 --> 01:41:00,899
I encourage you to make yourself at home.

2565
01:41:00,899 --> 01:41:03,139
And the door closes behind him

2566
01:41:03,139 --> 01:41:05,139
as you hear footsteps walking away.

2567
01:41:07,300 --> 01:41:08,300
What do you do?

2568
01:41:10,500 --> 01:41:14,699
Is it genuinely just like a room,

2569
01:41:15,899 --> 01:41:18,659
like a cell or what am I in?

2570
01:41:18,659 --> 01:41:21,819
As you begin to focus more, you feel around

2571
01:41:21,819 --> 01:41:25,619
and the ground doesn't feel like ground.

2572
01:41:25,619 --> 01:41:30,619
It has a soft, almost flesh feel to it.

2573
01:41:30,699 --> 01:41:33,859
And as you make your way around the room

2574
01:41:33,859 --> 01:41:35,699
that you feel you are in,

2575
01:41:35,699 --> 01:41:40,099
you run into jagged bars that surround you

2576
01:41:40,099 --> 01:41:44,059
and you find that you are in fact in a cell.

2577
01:41:44,979 --> 01:41:46,899
Make a wisdom saving throw.

2578
01:41:48,939 --> 01:41:51,539
Fuck, 11.

2579
01:41:51,539 --> 01:41:54,939
I have a plus six, still did not, didn't do good.

2580
01:41:54,939 --> 01:41:57,059
Okay, I would also like you

2581
01:41:57,059 --> 01:42:00,059
to roll percentile dice, please.

2582
01:42:00,059 --> 01:42:04,939
Okey-dokey, 39.

2583
01:42:04,980 --> 01:42:09,700
The wisdom saving throw was for overcoming madness.

2584
01:42:09,700 --> 01:42:13,780
You take a level of orcas madness.

2585
01:42:14,780 --> 01:42:17,220
Lipsinki Pip Diggins is compelled

2586
01:42:17,220 --> 01:42:19,300
to make the weak suffer.

2587
01:42:22,180 --> 01:42:24,260
So as this madness washes over,

2588
01:42:24,260 --> 01:42:27,420
you describe to me as best you can

2589
01:42:27,420 --> 01:42:32,060
how Lipsinki is feeling and dealing with this.

2590
01:42:32,060 --> 01:42:36,740
I almost wonder if she wouldn't sort of almost split.

2591
01:42:36,740 --> 01:42:41,740
Like this is already a person who is used to dealing

2592
01:42:42,180 --> 01:42:45,500
with creatures sort of speaking in her head from beyond

2593
01:42:45,500 --> 01:42:50,500
and I think maybe this level of grossness and trauma

2594
01:42:51,780 --> 01:42:56,780
split so she has, now there's a new evil Lipsinki.

2595
01:42:57,460 --> 01:42:59,980
But the nice one's still inside there

2596
01:43:00,020 --> 01:43:05,020
but she's compartmentalized these two, these two people.

2597
01:43:06,660 --> 01:43:11,300
As you sit and this washes over you,

2598
01:43:12,100 --> 01:43:17,100
you focus a little more on the room around you

2599
01:43:17,300 --> 01:43:21,260
and beyond the cell and you hear a soft mumbled voice

2600
01:43:21,260 --> 01:43:25,300
coming from another part of this jail

2601
01:43:25,300 --> 01:43:26,700
for lack of a better term.

2602
01:43:27,699 --> 01:43:30,979
It's tough to tell which direction

2603
01:43:30,979 --> 01:43:33,099
as any noise you feel kind of echoes

2604
01:43:33,099 --> 01:43:35,179
and bounces off the walls around you

2605
01:43:35,179 --> 01:43:36,779
and it's very disorienting.

2606
01:43:37,619 --> 01:43:38,979
What do you do or say?

2607
01:43:42,939 --> 01:43:44,579
Hello?

2608
01:43:44,579 --> 01:43:46,300
Is there somebody there?

2609
01:43:46,300 --> 01:43:47,899
Can I hear you?

2610
01:43:47,899 --> 01:43:48,739
Am I?

2611
01:43:50,179 --> 01:43:52,220
And I'm kind of like touching my head

2612
01:43:52,220 --> 01:43:56,099
cause I'm not even sure if I'm hearing it externally

2613
01:43:56,100 --> 01:43:59,260
or if it's someone internal or what I'm hearing.

2614
01:44:01,300 --> 01:44:05,700
As you do that you hear the voice become more clear

2615
01:44:05,700 --> 01:44:07,620
and the room begins to focus

2616
01:44:07,620 --> 01:44:10,500
as your eyes acclimatize to it

2617
01:44:10,500 --> 01:44:15,020
and you see a figure a distance away

2618
01:44:15,020 --> 01:44:18,060
glowing a soft gray blue

2619
01:44:18,980 --> 01:44:20,860
and the voice becomes clearer.

2620
01:44:20,860 --> 01:44:23,980
You hear them whispering to themselves

2621
01:44:23,980 --> 01:44:26,380
as the figure rocks back and forth

2622
01:44:27,580 --> 01:44:32,580
a soft oh boy, oh boy, oh boy

2623
01:44:37,140 --> 01:44:37,980
is heard.

