Sorry, those words came out of my mouth.

2650
01:45:53,460 --> 01:45:55,619
You wake up the next day.

2651
01:45:55,619 --> 01:45:57,980
You're missing your, you're missing your kidneys.

2652
01:45:57,980 --> 01:45:59,260
It's been a long time.

2653
01:45:59,260 --> 01:46:00,079
Nice bath.

2654
01:46:00,079 --> 01:46:00,920
I knew it.

2655
01:46:02,500 --> 01:46:04,140
There you go creating another fable.

2656
01:46:04,140 --> 01:46:05,539
That's all D&D is.

2657
01:46:05,539 --> 01:46:07,020
You wanted to.

2658
01:46:07,020 --> 01:46:09,980
Wait, you got a thing for things.

2659
01:46:09,980 --> 01:46:10,820
Yeah, I do.

2660
01:46:12,140 --> 01:46:13,260
Some say it's weird,

2661
01:46:13,260 --> 01:46:16,180
but I have a thing for things.

2662
01:46:16,180 --> 01:46:17,620
Don't look at my screen.

2663
01:46:17,620 --> 01:46:18,780
Don't look at my screen.

2664
01:46:18,780 --> 01:46:21,140
Don't, don't you look at my screen.

2665
01:46:21,140 --> 01:46:22,180
Don't you do it.

2666
